fits,</p><p class="">see <b>ACCRUAL OF BENEFITS</b></p><p class="indent2">* Plan year compensation,</p><p class="">see <b>NONDISCRIMINATION TESTING</b></p><p class="indent2">* Post-severance compensation</p><p class="indent3">- Benefit accrual/employer contribution allocations: inclusion of post-severance compensation in determination, <b><a href="/FullText/B001/CH_1A/CH_1A_SEC493#CH_1A_SEC493" target="_blank">1A.124</a></b></p><p class="indent3">- Deferrals under 401(k) arrangement from post-severance compensation, <b><a href="/FullText/B001/CH_11/CH_11_SEC170#CH_11_SEC170" target="_blank">11.44</a></b></p><p class="indent3">- Differential wage payments treated as active employee compensation (HEART Act rule), <b><a href="/FullText/B001/CH_1A/CH_1A_SEC389#CH_1A_SEC389" target="_blank">1A.89</a></b>, <b><a href="/FullText/B001/CH_3B/CH_3B_SEC376#CH_3B_SEC376" target="_blank">3B.134</a></b></p><p class="indent3">- Nondiscrimination testing issues under IRC &#167;414(s), <b><a href="/FullText/B001/CH_1A/CH_1A_SEC467#CH_1A_SEC467" target="_blank">1A.117</a></b></p><p class="indent3">- Post-severance compensation generally <b>excluded</b> from section 415 compensation, <b><a href="/FullText/B001/CH_1A/CH_1A_SEC376#CH_1A_SEC376" target="_blank">1A.87</a></b></p><p class="indent3">- Types of post-severance compensation includible in section 415 compensation</p><p class="indent4">&#9670; Disability: certain salary continuation payments eligible to be included, <b><a href="/FullText/B001/CH_1A/CH_1A_SEC391#CH_1A_SEC391" target="_blank">1A.90</a></b></p><p class="indent4">&#9670; Inclusion of certain amounts paid within 2&#189; months after severance (or end of year in which severance occurs, if later), <b><a href="/FullText/B001/CH_1A/CH_1A_SEC381#CH_1A_SEC381" target="_blank">1A.88</a></b></p><p class="indent4">&#9670; Military service: inclusion of certain salary continuation payments eligible to be included, <b><a href="/FullText/B001/CH_1A/CH_1A_SEC340#CH_1A_SEC340" tar